r />\n樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最緊要踏出第一步"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:40:07.000Z","msg":"就嚟試下坐空車 練習下...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:57:33.000Z","msg":"揾方法/機會 盡量坐到第一行/坐前D<br />\n咁你同司機既距離越近, 中間隔少D人 你就會大D勇氣嗌有落"},{"pid":"b6f815b3ac79dbf1484826eb3c8c526fa0d3b3b0","tid":2437451,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T08:07:35.000Z","msg":"基本嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人等過馬路好唔自在，隻手唔知做乜好<br />\n多數扮講電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee565472d4f3eae73e1cf1d4bed2f96b7f6b54f","tid":2437451,"uid":158145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6f815b3ac79dbf1484826eb3c8c526fa0d3b3b0","tid":2437451,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T08:07:35.000Z","msg":"基本嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人等過馬路好唔自在，隻手唔知做乜好<br />\n多數扮講電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:37:48.000Z","msg":"搭lift會咁<br />\n咁多人塞喺一個地方會好緊張<br />\n我會扮講電話"},{"pid":"a3954f4e0f515b4afa99fd5eb141bffce7ceda99","tid":2437451,"uid":40940,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T10:55:01.000Z","msg":"我已經早5分鐘練定嗌有落，<br />\n係心入面嗌左過百次，我諗我當時既表情就好似林雪練瀨尿牛丸咁樣。<br />\n唉，但唔知係咪練得太多，練到反噬左我心智，我居然早左一個站走火嗌左岀黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n 有條友都比我殺到操手不及，大驚之下嗌 「喂，XX過左未？我要落渦」我估佢都係道上既朋友，一時失心瘋亂嗌左岀黎，因為佢個站仲後過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   最後架車停左，我落左車避柒，一回頭佢又留左車，兩個戇鳩一齊行去我哋想去既站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d086ff080aba6738bf156218fe49fbd9928b49","tid":2437451,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T23:27:59.000Z","msg":"有 你"},{"pid":"e410e65fc5f167786f916c86a6e7f476a6ece69d","tid":2437451,"uid":42430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T23:47:25.000Z","msg":"埋站前我會走去司機耳邊細細聲講有落"}]}